								<p> 50k downloads of extensions combined<br><a href='https://atom.io/packages/autocomplete-elixir'>Elixir Autocomplete</a> - Over 40k downloads. Formerly             the most popular Atom Elixir extension for over 2 years.             <br>             <a href='https://atom.io/packages/autocomplete-elixir'>Erlang Autocomplete</a> - Over 10k downloads. The most             popular Atom Erlang extension. </p>
